::: proof-title
Null / Smaller / Reduced model
:::

::: proof-cont
$LE = \beta_0 + \beta_1 FLR + \epsilon$
:::
:::
:::

::: {.column width="45%"}
::: definition
::: def-title
Alternative / Larger / Full model
:::

::: def-cont
$LE = \beta_0 + \beta_1 FLR + \beta_2 FS + \epsilon$
:::
